{"tid":418653,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊分享下成份簡單又好用嘅護膚品","createTime":"2017-09-29T17:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T15:51:02.000Z","uid":39753,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"43cb37565b5301ef00cc63e12a64a2184031fc06","tid":418653,"uid":39753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:36:38.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇巴絲同我一樣 <br />\n對護膚品既成份好執著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上有paraben, PEG, 酒精, 人工香料, 矽靈, mit既護膚品都唔會用<br />\n<br />\n以前試過唔理成份 亂敷一大堆cheap cheap mask 搞到而家變敏感肌 又焗粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住搵啲連濕疹都用得既牌子<br />\n上網見cetaphil cleanser 好多人讚<br />\n買左枝 之後先發現原來又係有paraben既<br />\n<br />\n而家暫時搵到成份真係比較簡單既護膚品 得呢幾隻<br />\n<br />\n1. Physiogel Moisture Therapy Lotion<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hvcgarfx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhvcgarfx&h=89b47592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/24fmg75i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F24fmg75i&h=f9ee552c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. Etude House Manuka Honey Mask<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yo7ulg0x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyo7ulg0x&h=a9c82a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/shj846le\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fshj846le&h=1046c9fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然有paraben 但暫時未搵到代替品 照用住先既：<br />\n<br />\n肌研保濕化妝水<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b0fzg73k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb0fzg73k&h=db8c2d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我自己識得既護膚品牌子唔多<br />\n都係上網爬文睇人介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外 而家網上好多post都係收錢廣告  加上好多宣稱天然/醫美既牌子product其實都係有刺激性成份 <br />\n要搵到枝岩用既真係難過搵男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望呢個post可以大家一齊真心分享<br />\n下 平貴都無所謂 最緊要好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0736487621ad804e4216f19145f14204cce6d817","tid":418653,"uid":19072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad7263237c06820e048a565cc86a21d1e138456f","tid":418653,"uid":39753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>H2SO4</blockquote><br />\n喂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8dfdbc7421d4867c3d46205079798472c310ebb","tid":418653,"uid":39753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:52:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2c7acc3e3493ef315b1e55660b5676c4cf7f3aa","tid":418653,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T20:45:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2eeecff05ef077191c3d663416c9d052fd99d84","tid":418653,"uid":39753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:25:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9e52d5e9e9ca3ab21438b880a0ec5e38440d3073","tid":418653,"uid":19242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:27:56.000Z","msg":"之前用the ordinary敏感 係咁生粒粒 而家toner同moisturiser用ad+ 佢舒緩同抗炎好好 依家都冇點生粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排用過好用又冇sls又平既cleanser: freeplus mild soap(起好多泡)、acure sensitive facial cleanser(起少少泡)<br />\n<br />\n仲有物理防曬：ad+(低spf)、fancl、nov(spf50有啲厚)、遲啲再試埋elta md<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04fde3cd2ffd4b2ea899b88ff6a51e069222a55","tid":418653,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:32:07.000Z","msg":"一定係the ordinary啦<br />\n性價比又高"},{"pid":"5004bd22e11b7f4e1a9cdfff982745a867ba39e6","tid":418653,"uid":39753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T0